ull, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "One should observe fast on the 1st Thursday of Mahe Rajab and between the Maghrib and Isha Namaz, recite 12-rakat namaz (in form of 2-2-rakats). In each rakat after <Surah Fateha> recite <Surah Qadr> 3 times and <Surah Ikhlaas> 12 times.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Mahe Rajab ke 1st Thursday ko Roza rakkhe aur Namaz Maghrebain ke darmiyaan 12 rakat namaz, 2x2 rakat karke, har rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad 3 martaba <Surah Qadr> aur <Surah Ikhlaas> 12 martaba padhe.", "UrduDescription": "اس با برکت نماز کی ترکیب یہ ہے کہ ماہ ِرجب کی پہلی جمعرات کو روزہ رکھے اور شب ِجمعہ میں مغرب و عشا کے درمیان ب۱۲کعت دو دو رکعت کر کے نماز پڑھے کہ ہر رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد ۳ مرتبہ <سورۂ قدر> اور ۱۲ مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> پڑھے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, 